The article is a statement by the President on the Paycheck Fairness Act. The President expresses disappointment in Senate Republicans for not allowing a vote on the legislation, which aims to strengthen the Equal Pay Act and provide more tools for women to fight pay discrimination. The President emphasizes that women continue to earn less than men for the same work and pledges to continue fighting for equal pay and rebuilding the economy so that hard work is rewarded and everyone has a fair chance to succeed.